{"tid":2024482,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[大新聞]霍格華茲宣怖開辨Asso課程，有冇麻瓜想做後門巫師？","createTime":"2020-05-19T15:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T09:43:22.000Z","uid":353419,"like":52,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb0a2d63ef368adfe607e6f1c911c937452451f","tid":2024482,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLRAqDd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLRAqDd.png&h=146b7c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Q&amp;A :</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問(1)：咩係魔法Asso仔（魔專生）?</span><br />\n<br />\n答(1)：本來天生識魔法既青少年，會自動俾魔法學校取錄，但近年各國魔法學校開辨左Asso課程，俾天生唔識魔法既麻瓜學習魔法，如果GPA高分，有機會由魔專生升格為正式魔法學生。其實魔法Asso課程開辨左十年，但外國麻瓜讀比較多，因為暫時係香港好少麻瓜知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問(2)：入讀魔法Asso有咩門檻?</span><br />\n<br />\n答(2)：基本上冇，學店來的，有錢你就讀到，不過魔法Asso仔學費仲貴過正式魔法學生，不過魔法部有Grant Loan，你需要去妖精銀行開個户口先。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問(3)：萬一升唔番上去。魔法Asso畢業有咩工作出路？</span><br />\n<br />\n答(3)：唔洗擔心，魔法Asso仔就業率90%以上，畢業生工作主要係：九又四份三月台車站站員，阿茲卡班高級文員，同埋斜角巷巫師袍Sales<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>問(4.)：如果爛GPA，又唔想工作，有咩其他學校可以升？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n答(4.)：可以入讀私立魔法學校既自資課程，例如巴西既卡斯特羅布舍 （魔法恒大），烏干達既瓦加度（魔法IVE），不過同學質素極差，連魔仗都唔識點渣，每屆三巫鬥法大賽都無佢地學校份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGGAqDP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGGAqDP.jpg&h=ca4b40d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>魔法Asso學校介紹：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.霍格華茲附屬學院（魔法Space)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n簡介：唔好以為讀Hogwart Space就上得番Hogwart，你要拎好高GPA先有機會入到，亦冇機會係上圖既霍格華茲校舍返學。魔法Asso仔要係另一個校舍上堂，係個荒廢工廠大廈，仲要無球場玩魁地奇，掃把課仲係去隔離鎮個爛地上堂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46yyWMX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46yyWMX.jpg&h=8e020b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.伊爾弗莫尼專上學院(魔法CC)</span><br />\n<br />\n美國既正氣師（當年佢地追捕過葛林戴華德），大部份都係依間學校畢業，而佢開辨既Asso課程，被譽為魔法Asso界一哥，升學率非常高。英國霍格華茲，法國波巴洞魔法學院等等名校都傾向收番魔法CC仔女，學校設施都非常優良，不過競爭好大，太多勁人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qWTCD0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqWTCD0n.jpg&h=5af11cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.魔法所專上學院 （魔法CIE)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n位於日本既魔法學校，擅長符咒式神陰陽術，但無論係魔法Asso仔還是正式魔法學生，都係大陸留學生居多，近年甚至越黎越大陸化，用簡體字學魔法，掃把巫師袍都係大陸制造，不過無可否認，大陸學生魔法成績好撚高分，全部都係考試機器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N2sgM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N2sgM7.jpg&h=ac93df38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpq5NTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffpq5NTQ.jpg&h=4bc6f237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學系：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">神科：</span></strong><br />\n1 黑魔法防禦術<br />\n2 變形學<br />\n3 符咒學<br />\n4 魔藥學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HP8nP7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHP8nP7f.jpg&h=db9315c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">水泡科：</span><br />\n古代神秘文字研究<br />\n麻瓜研究<br />\n算命學<br />\n占卜學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJN71d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJN71d1.jpg&h=1a7f9342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCiCD0K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCiCD0K.jpg&h=3a2aa193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">乞食科：</span><br />\n魔法史<br />\n奇獸飼育學<br />\n天文學<br />\n藥草學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">魔法界Non-Jupas 面試情報：</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2bdckS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2bdckS.jpg&h=ecaa3622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 葛林戴華德讀過既德姆蘭學校，最鐘意識黑魔法既同學，聽聞如果你面試用黑魔法，佢會加分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTZyckX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTZyckX.jpg&h=a68a08b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.波巴洞魔法學院係女校，唔收男人，上屆有連登毒撚嘗試用變身劑扮女人面試，最後被永久Black List左。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECm1mem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECm1mem.png&h=cb64df44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.霍格華茲既麥教授面試好好人，會比貼士你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y0axsUr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0axsUr.jpg&h=e74252b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.霍格華茲既黑魔法防御術係最難入神科，石內卜教授面試果陣，要考生互相隻抽Battle。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">（歡迎各位魔法Asso仔交流校園心得同埋面試情報，正式魔法學生勿踩場）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"c1cbedafa51d47627b50fde99d33d27ae8f0b9db","tid":2024482,"uid":7551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"ddc5150674bf1541a08d625d5785da9829bc0401","tid":2024482,"uid":197563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvPKjwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvPKjwu.jpg&h=c3c94a29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d9bd1a4764e24f89cc0f9babff1a055ae6efb27","tid":2024482,"uid":215700,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:22:34.000Z","msg":"雖然篇文好on9但樓主真係好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccb3ac53bc727232112972f827d8395ea33244a","tid":2024482,"uid":271250,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:25:27.000Z","msg":"「掃把巫師袍都係大陸制造」，上年先有幾單學生騎騎下掃把爆炸嘅事件喎，仲水人入去讀。"},{"pid"